'''''Eight for Aduba-3: The Saga of the Starhoppers''''' was a [[Holodocumentary|holo-doc]] made by [[Tri-Nebula Entertainment]] on the events surrounding [[Han Solo/Legends|Han Solo's]] successful defense of the [[Onacra]] village on [[Aduba-3/Legends|Aduba-3]].

==History==
The holo-doc was their third feature on Han Solo and proved to be a moderate hit.

The [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel Alliance]] historian [[Voren Na'al/Legends|Voren Na'al]] felt the holo-doc was so successful that the people of Aduba-3 had begun to believe it was totally factual. He felt this hindered his own efforts to uncover the actual events that took place there.

